    <abstract>
      <t>This document describes a method for clients using [HTTP-MESSAGE-SIGNATURES] to advertise their signing keys. It defines a key directory format based on JWKS as defined in Section 5 of [JWK], as well as new HTTP Method Context to allow for in-band key discovery.</t>
    </abstract>
